high_descs: turn around, go to counter with microwave to the right
open microwave, take out potato in front of black mug in microwave, close microwave
turn around, go past counter to sink to the right
place potato in front of bottle in sink, turn on water, turn off water, pick up potato from sink
turn around, go to counter with microwave to the right
place potato on right side of gray plate in microwave, close microwave
take the potato from the microwave
take the potato to the sink
rinse the potato in the sink then remove
take the potato back to the microwave
put the potato in the microwave
Turn left, go to the microwave on the counter to the left.
Take the egg on the right out of the microwave.
Bring the egg to the left, keep going around the center island to the left and go to the sink on the other side of the island.
Wash the egg in the sink.
Bring the washed egg back to the microwave on the other side of the room.
Put the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed egg in the microwave.
